{"tid":1543382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"資訊科技界240人種票 廉署只起訴17人","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:45:35.000Z","uid":165683,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"075c818f76c6806436abe6b92391c12923e4b724","tid":1543382,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478946-20190905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478946-20190905.htm&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=676345c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478946-20190905.htm&h=19901cb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478946-20190905.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n何解240人輸入虛假專業資格及學歷資料,36人收賄，只有17人被起訴<br />\n完全沒有阻嚇其他人種票之效<br />\n<br />\n廉署星期一至昨日先後起訴17人，涉嫌與2016年立法會資訊科技界選舉賄選及種票有關。<br />\n<br />\n17個被告明日在東區裁判法院應訊，7人與的士司機從業員總會有關，其中45歲的士司機從業員總會幹事雷亞福，有5名親戚一同被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n其中14名被告，共被控1項串謀在選舉中作出舞弊行為提供利益予他人、1項串謀詐騙，以及10項在選舉中作出舞弊行為接受利益。其中1項指4名被告涉嫌一同與其他身分不詳的人串謀，向<span style=\"color: red;\">36人提供每人1000元</span>，作為他們投票予某候選人的誘因。"},{"pid":"05f24382451fcd1a9c00c17142825168f92c53f7","tid":1543382,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht